						               													<description>User Summary:&amp;#10;The Wasteland is a a 22 pages scenario book only available to the subscribers of Ambush Alley Games Special Operation Group, a membership system that grants discounts and access to exclusive contents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Unlike the previous year exclusive scenario book, Under The Black Flag, that was only for Ambush Alley, this booklet contains scenarios for the three core Ambush Alley Games rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The three scenarios details engagements of the forces of the &amp;quot;Barony&amp;quot; of Harlin's Corner, a small town in a post-apocalypse USA.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Scenario 1 - In the Rat's Alley - For Ambush Alley&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;        A Squad of Baron's Rangers find themselves in the middle of a Raider's Camp, they must fight their way out running and gunning! The Raider's mission is much simpler, kill them all!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Scenario 2 - Agony in Stony Places - For Force on Force&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;        A Small force of Harlin Corner must resist the onslaught of a scouting force from the Ominious Central Republic long enough for the reinforcements from the Corner to arrive. The Central republican forces must try to sweep away the defenders and get closer to the Barony, failing that, they must report to the Republic command the strength of the local resistance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Scenario 3 - Fear in a Handful of Dust - For Ambush Z&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;        A simple mission to recover a cache of medical supplies from a wasteland city turns into a nightmare as the Baron's rangers are attacked by zombies!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The booklet also contains information regarding the Barony Forces, Central Republic forces, Raiders, Zombies, Mutants and Grey Aliens to design other scenarios in the setting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The booklet is available only as a download.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
